text: Hi <@U8THBCFC4> a <https://community.HubSpot.com/t5/Blog-Website-Page-Publishing/Hide-this-module-not-clickable/m-p/721406#M7520|thread> popped up in the community where clicking the hide icon in the new Content tab layout was not hiding the module, but opening the module to edit - I'm not sure if this is related to the theme/module or the new layout and thought you might have additional insight.
